org.hayabaya.datarelated

Class Results

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hayabaya.datarelated.Results

  • public class Results
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores all of the data that is relevant to the profiling project. It gathers the data and makes it possible to write it to disk in csv files.

    By calling WriteResults the 2D array is written to disk as a text file with the naming convention results.[data type].[operation].[experiment repetion].csv
